Can I ask for a pair of eyes on #9588? This is almost trivial to review (just moves a file, very simple diff).

This is a pre-requisite for #9565 (splitting MFDeriv, a large 2200 lines file); I was asked for split out the move - and maybe the reviewer got distracted by Lean together then.

This was approved, but accrued a merge conflict. I just merged master. Can somebody kick this PR again, please?
I've delegated it, please wait for CI to finish and then merge it. Thanks!
